30:48.333 --> 30:49.966
Talk to me.

30:50.034 --> 30:52.001
Found out Sasquatch
took a dive in the fight.

30:53.304 --> 30:55.771
That fucking asshole. You kidding me?

30:55.840 --> 30:58.207
Mm-hmm, that was pretty
much my response too.

30:59.978 --> 31:03.179
I feel totally responsible for
you guys losing all your money.

31:03.248 --> 31:05.047
It's fine.

31:05.116 --> 31:07.216
You didn't know, right?

31:08.520 --> 31:10.920
I would try and keep this from
reaching Davis's ears, though.

31:10.921 --> 31:12.655
Got it.

31:12.724 --> 31:14.891
Why are you telling me all of this?

31:14.960 --> 31:16.840
You trying to get me
back? Is that what this is?

31:16.841 --> 31:17.960
No.

31:18.029 --> 31:19.409
You're still married to Alvarez,

31:19.464 --> 31:20.997
and she still needs that green card.

31:21.065 --> 31:22.999
We can't be seen together.

31:23.067 --> 31:24.267
- Ever.
- If you recall,

31:24.335 --> 31:26.235
we were pretty good at
not being seen together.

31:26.304 --> 31:29.172
Not nearly as good as
we thought we were.

31:29.240 --> 31:31.941
I don't know if I can accept that.

31:32.010 --> 31:34.343
Maybe it's time to.

31:37.916 --> 31:39.949
You're late.

31:41.119 --> 31:43.453
Hey man, I need to re-up on those M18s.

31:43.522 --> 31:45.888
- Yeah, okay.
- Thanks.

31:47.725 --> 31:50.493
The bullet shattered your humerus.

31:50.562 --> 31:51.994
Now I regret to inform you

31:52.063 --> 31:53.796
that it's not going to
be an easy recovery.

31:53.865 --> 31:55.465
You're probably going to be dealing with

31:55.494 --> 31:57.334
the residual effects
for the rest of your life.

31:57.335 --> 31:58.801
And that's the good news?

31:58.870 --> 32:00.570
- In this instance, yes.
- Hm.

32:00.638 --> 32:03.172
- You wanted to see me, sir?
- Yes, Corporal.

32:03.241 --> 32:05.274
I need the Secretary's
scans and medical chart

32:05.343 --> 32:07.510
sent directly on to Walter
Reed Medical Center.

32:07.579 --> 32:09.845
You're the only one that I
trust to make sure it happens.

32:09.914 --> 32:11.514
- On it, sir.
- Very good.

32:11.583 --> 32:12.848
Try to get some rest.

32:12.917 --> 32:14.884
You've got a long journey ahead of you.

32:14.953 --> 32:16.986
Corporal.

32:18.556 --> 32:20.056
Yes, sir?

32:20.124 --> 32:23.626
- May I ask you a question?
- Of course.

32:23.695 --> 32:26.262
Do you know why you're here?

32:26.331 --> 32:28.431
To transfer your scans
and medical chart to...

32:28.499 --> 32:31.567
No, I mean in Afghanistan.

32:31.636 --> 32:34.904
Do you know why you're
here in Afghanistan?

32:36.507 --> 32:39.175
I believe we're here to stop
the threat of terrorism.

32:39.244 --> 32:41.777
And do you think that goal
is being accomplished?

32:41.846 --> 32:43.446
I can't really tell, sir.

32:45.783 --> 32:47.984
Neither can I,

32:48.052 --> 32:50.419
and that's sort of my job.

32:51.956 --> 32:53.396
I'm sure you'll figure it out, sir.

32:53.397 --> 32:56.464
That makes one of us.

32:58.463 --> 33:00.129
Is that all, sir?

33:00.198 --> 33:03.399
Unfortunately that just
about covers it, Corporal.

33:23.641 --> 33:25.721
Those are some gorgeous
looking rugs you got there.

33:25.722 --> 33:27.510
Yeah, my mom's a collector,

33:27.578 --> 33:30.246
so figured I'd surprise
her for her birthday.

33:30.314 --> 33:33.182
Go ahead and fill these out
while I get these weighed.

33:33.251 --> 33:36.018
- Where they off to?
- Chicago, Illinois.

33:39.690 --> 33:42.091
Sergeant Davis.

33:42.159 --> 33:43.425
What do you need, Private?

33:43.494 --> 33:46.495
I need a money order for $5,000.

33:46.564 --> 33:49.365
Tell me you didn't buy
one of those cars.

33:50.501 --> 33:52.801
Yeah, well, I... I
can't tell you I didn't

33:52.870 --> 33:54.436
because I did.

33:54.505 --> 33:57.072
Petrocelli, those
dealerships are a scam.

33:57.141 --> 33:58.941
Everybody knows it.

33:59.010 --> 34:00.676
They set up shop here on the base

34:00.745 --> 34:03.646
to target naive young soldiers
on their first deployment.

34:03.714 --> 34:05.180
Why would they do that?

34:05.249 --> 34:07.483
Because the car companies
pay off somebody

34:07.552 --> 34:09.885
at the Pentagon, and kids
like you got nothing better

34:09.954 --> 34:12.321
to spend your money on out
here in the middle of the desert.

34:12.389 --> 34:16.391
The car salesman gave me
a $500 military discount,

34:16.460 --> 34:19.295
and a very low interest rate of 20%.

34:19.931 --> 34:22.431
That's not a low interest rate.

34:23.301 --> 34:25.261
Uh, give me a sec for
that money order, Private.

34:25.262 --> 34:26.569
And, uh, Sergeant,

34:26.637 --> 34:28.871
you're looking at nearly
100 pounds on those rugs.

34:28.900 --> 34:30.179
It's gonna be pricey to send 'em

34:30.181 --> 34:32.308
all the way back to the States.

34:32.376 --> 34:35.844
Wait, you found Buckley's rugs?

34:36.581 --> 34:38.213
You sending these back to his family?

34:38.282 --> 34:39.722
- Well, well...
- That is so awesome.

34:39.750 --> 34:42.952
You are a really good
person, Sergeant Davis.

34:43.020 --> 34:44.699
And I... I don't mean
just on the outside,

34:44.701 --> 34:47.467
I mean in here on the inside.

34:48.559 --> 34:51.226
A really good person.

34:53.130 --> 34:55.030
You mind if I just do this over here?

34:55.099 --> 34:57.466
Sure, lemme just look
how much this'll cost.

34:57.535 --> 34:59.301
You said it's going
to Chicago, Illinois?

34:59.370 --> 35:00.703
Yeah.

35:00.771 --> 35:02.471
That's not where Buckley lives.

35:02.540 --> 35:04.173
He's from Texas.

35:04.241 --> 35:07.009
He actually has
extended family all over.

35:07.078 --> 35:09.478
Huh. Really?

35:09.547 --> 35:11.347
Yeah.

35:11.415 --> 35:13.282
Hmm. Cool.

35:14.251 --> 35:17.119
You know what, uh, tell them I said hey.

35:18.556 --> 35:21.290
Not a day goes by that I
don't think about their son.

35:22.727 --> 35:24.627
I will.

35:43.814 --> 35:46.815
Hey.

35:46.884 --> 35:48.584
Could you look up the address

35:48.653 --> 35:51.854
of a John Buckley in Texas who was KIA?

35:51.922 --> 35:54.490
I wanna reroute the shipment.

36:17.949 --> 36:19.449
Here you go, sir.

36:20.551 --> 36:22.785
You wanted to see us, sir?

36:22.853 --> 36:24.319
Yes.

36:24.388 --> 36:26.889
I want to thank you
both for saving my life.

36:26.957 --> 36:28.957
It's what we get paid for, sir.

36:29.026 --> 36:30.793
America would be better off

36:30.861 --> 36:33.395
if more immigrants
were like you, Sergeant.

36:33.464 --> 36:35.631
- They are, sir.
- I know.

36:35.700 --> 36:38.434
That said though, if even
one foreign national

36:38.502 --> 36:40.969
has ulterior motives amongst your rank,

36:41.038 --> 36:42.304
that's one too many.

36:42.373 --> 36:44.073
After what happened at Fort Hood,

36:44.141 --> 36:45.541
we can't have that risk anymore.

36:45.609 --> 36:48.010
If you don't mind my saying so,

36:48.079 --> 36:49.912
that is seriously flawed logic.

36:49.980 --> 36:51.947
Not from where I'm standing.

36:52.016 --> 36:53.582
Sorry to hear that, sir.

36:53.651 --> 36:55.951
Um, the helicopter's ready for you, sir.

36:56.020 --> 36:57.753
Right.

36:59.190 --> 37:01.990
Thank you for your service, Sergeant.

37:02.059 --> 37:03.759
I wish you the best.

37:05.129 --> 37:06.849
If you really wanted
to wish her the best,

37:06.850 --> 37:08.797
you'd help her!

37:08.866 --> 37:10.265
When everyone wants to know

37:10.334 --> 37:11.767
what the hell went down out there,

37:11.836 --> 37:13.235
I will not tell them

37:13.304 --> 37:15.771
that your little joyride
ended in the death

37:15.840 --> 37:17.406
of my good friend.

37:17.475 --> 37:21.276
I will instead speak well of you both

37:21.345 --> 37:24.880
because I admire your wife's
bravery and good sense.

37:26.717 --> 37:31.120
You are a lucky man, Sergeant,
in more ways than one.

37:47.505 --> 37:49.838
Sorry.

37:58.115 --> 38:01.583
Here I was trying to save you,
and you end up saving me.

38:01.652 --> 38:03.685
One of these days we're
gonna have to learn

38:03.754 --> 38:05.788
to save ourselves.

38:05.856 --> 38:08.290
Yeah.

38:24.408 --> 38:25.974
Welcome to our family.

38:26.043 --> 38:27.409
Your bonus check will clear

38:27.478 --> 38:28.878
as soon as your paperwork processes

38:28.913 --> 38:32.281
and we receive proper
documentation for your ETS.

38:32.349 --> 38:35.551
Just a few months left.

38:35.619 --> 38:37.539
You're about to come into
a great deal of money

38:37.607 --> 38:39.967
for doing what you're already
doing for practically nothing.

38:39.968 --> 38:42.615
That's the fucking plan.

38:43.561 --> 38:45.227
All right, we'll be in touch.

38:49.366 --> 38:50.866
I'd love to be a fly on the wall

38:50.935 --> 38:52.367
when he breaks the news to Roback.

38:52.436 --> 38:54.269
What makes you so
sure he hasn't already?

38:54.338 --> 38:55.971
I'm sure.

